ing\ncases, and less than 10% pointwise $L_1$ error for most cases, verifying such\ngeneralization claims. Finally, the CRAN predictions offer similar wave\ncharacteristic patterns to the target solutions indicating not only their\ngeneralization but also their kinematical consistency.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Apr 2022 07:09:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Oct 2022 10:07:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-12"}
