, we conclude that the broad QFP wave train was a\nlarge-amplitude fast-mode magnetosonic wave or a weak shock driven by some\nnon-linear energy release processes in the accompanying flare.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Apr 2022 08:07:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 14 Apr 2022 01:11:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-11"}
