ndences between three sets of different\nmathematical concepts that are usually thought of separately as polytopes,\nsubgroups of $SU(2)$ and $ADE$ Lie algebras. Here we connect them explicitly\nand in a unified way by thinking of them as three different sets of root\nsystems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Apr 2022 11:20:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-13"}
