equence, a novel dynamic survival approach is proposed in\nthis work for the monitoring of potassium in heart failure. The proposed\nwavelet landmark method shows promising results revealing the prognostic role\nof short-term oscillations, according to their different duration, and\nachieving higher performances in predicting survival probability based on\npotassium over time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Apr 2022 15:09:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Apr 2022 11:55:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 14 Jul 2022 10:20:56 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 13 Mar 2023 14:37:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-14"}
